snippet.title: Best VGM 1228 - Call of Duty : Black Ops II - Outer Club Solar (Shadows)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3 / Wii U / PC
Call of Duty : Black Ops II  (2012)
Outer Club Solar (Shadows)
Brian Tuey
